        "timestamp": "2018-09-11 22:36:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThe current jobs don't work, and haven't worked. This cleans it up.  Basically, we have two directories inside vnfsdk/ice: ice-server and validation-scripts.  It only works if you run tox from the top level (vnfsdk/ice), but it breaks if you try run tox from inside one of the subdirectories.  This moves the job up to the top level, which should measure coverage from both subdirectories (local evidence works).",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
