        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-09-11 23:02:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nLet's not remove the INFO file job. \n\nThis one is still working as expected. I just verified a dummy change and works as expected:\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/view/vnfsdk/job/vnfsdk-ice-info-yaml-verify/5/console\n\nThanks a ton!",
